      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and performance. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers an exceptional balance of value and quality for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience the refined handling and enduring appeal of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
