    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility, showing in excellent mechanical shape with a comprehensive service history. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though minor road-wear is visible upon close inspection, consistent with careful use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains supple and smoke-free, with all power features, seat heaters, and navigation functioning flawlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires are in solid standing for many miles to come. This is a reliable, turn-key luxury SUV for the discerning buyer who values a well-documented history.",
      "price": 36850.0,
